<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>내 정보 - MyMarket</title>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">

    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">

    <style>
        body {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
        }

        .profile-card {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        .info-label {
            width: 120px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #495057;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <nav class="navbar navbar-dark bg-dark mb-5">
        <div class="container">
            <a href="/" class="navbar-brand fw-bold">🛒 MyMarket</a>
            <div>
                <a href="/" class="btn btn-outline-light btn-sm">홈으로</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <div class="container">
        <div class="card shadow profile-card">
            <div class="card-header bg-primary text-white">
                <h3 class="mb-0">내 정보 보기</h3>
            </div>

            <div class="card-body p-4">
                <div class="mb-3 d-flex">
                    <div class="info-label">회원 번호</div>
                    <div><%= profile.id %></div>
                </div>

                <div class="mb-3 d-flex">
                    <div class="info-label">아이디</div>
                    <div><%= profile.userId %></div>
                </div>

                <hr>

                <div class="alert alert-info small">
                    비밀번호는 보안상 화면에 표시하지 않습니다.
                </div>

                <div class="d-flex justify-content-end gap-2">
                    <a href="/" class="btn btn-secondary">
                        메인으로
                    </a>

                    <a href="/auth/profile/edit" class="btn btn-warning">
                        정보 수정
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>